<html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>TOEIC Results</title></head><body><h1>TOEIC SPEAKING RESULTS</h1><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-64.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Mental Health</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is mental health as important as physical health?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is mental health as important as physical health? (tinh thần vs vật lí)
I think that they are equally important. When you are in good mental condition you will have more balanced life. You eat, sleep and do better. That is the inspirantion to do anything you want. It makes you happier. 
-> digestion (n) -> immune systems (n) -> overal health (n).
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-64.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Mental Health</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What do you do for stress?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What do you do for stress?
When i am in stress.
1. leave everything behind.
2. turn off my mobile phone
3. go to the bed and have a deep sleep.
4. this helps me to disconnect from the world. and recharge the batterry.

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-64.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Mental Health</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should we talk more about feelings?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should we talk more about feelings?
1. I think we should
2. sometimes, we should look back to realise what is happening inside us and repair the hurt of feelings. 
3. It is a great way to be honest with ourself so we can have a leassons, understand our feelings and give up for our mistakes.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-65.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Online Shopping</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How often do you shop online?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How often do you shop online ? Why ?
-> I shop online everyday. I love to shop for comestics, daily goods, new clothes, ... because shopping is convinient. It has many options to choose. Every products have price tags on it, i can look for items from different store, i do not have to move to the shop in person. It saves a lot of time. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-65.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Online Shopping</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is the best thing about it?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is the best thing about it? Online Shopping
-> The best thing is that i can buy the products at home without moving. It is very convinient and time-saving for me because here, in Ha Noi, the traffics are crowded , polluted and noisy. There are many accidents  

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-65.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Online Shopping</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it safe?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it safe ? Online Shopping.
Yes, of course. 
1. It is refunding service. It can return the products.
2. If i receive the fake products, i can report the shops. 
3. Finally, the items often have guarantees -> I can unbox the products for checking.

 </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-66.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fast Food</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like fast food?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like fast food?
-> Not really, in the past, i used to like fast foods when i was a child because they were very delicious and convinient. However, i care more about my health now so i rarely have them.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-66.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fast Food</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is it healthy?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is it healthy ?  Fast Food
No, Fast Food is unhelathy. because fastfood has preservative (n): chất bảo quản to keep the foods longer. It overcontaints sugar and oil. It can cause heart disease, obesity. (overweight).
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-66.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Fast Food</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Why is it popular?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Why is it popular? Fast Food.
First, it is cheap and convinient. It is varying from sizes, types, favours, so it has many options to choose ..and . There are many stores i can buy it easily. Finally, they are delicious. People can try on new foods that they normally do not have at home.

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-67.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Artificial Intelligence</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you use AI tools?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you use AI tools ?. 
Yes, of course. 
Because they are very convinient and useful. AI can act like mentor for example, i can ask ChatGPT for any questions, advices and AI will repsonse quickly with good answers. It is for free and i can access it anywhere anytime. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-67.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Artificial Intelligence</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Will AI change education?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Will AI change education?
Not entirely. 
I think Ai has two sides.
On positive side, they can be an useful sources of knowledge. We can look for information quiclier and easiler.
On negative side, we can overdepend on AI, if you meet difficult questions and you always ask AI, it has bad effects to your brain. You will be lazy to think. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-67.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Artificial Intelligence</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is a risk of AI?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is a risk of AI?
I think AI will replace people in the future because AI can do a lot of jobs wtih higher productivity from caculation, looking for information and writing articles. From that, many people will lose their jobs. The government should control the AI. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-68.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Ocean Life</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like the sea?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like the sea?
-> Yes, absolutely, sea remains my favourite because sea is peaceful so whenever i see it feel relaxed. I can also practise many interesting activities on the beaches like lie on the sand, have sunbath and look at the wave. It is memoriable.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-68.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Ocean Life</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is your favorite sea creature?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite sea creature?
-> I love Dolphin. because it is very smart and friendly. I have read many articles about it's heroic actions like It save a lot of people when they are in accidents on the beach. I also can see dophin in aquarium to see it plays with the balls.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-68.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Ocean Life</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is ocean pollution a problem?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is ocean pollution a problem?
-> Yes, it is one of most urging problems in the world because ocean is overpolluted with rubbishs and oil. Many sea creatures are endangered because of this. It also affects resident's life near the beach so i think government should take actions to control this. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-69.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: City vs Countryside</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Where do you prefer to live?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Where do you prefer to live ? City vs Countryside
-> I prefer to live in the countryside but now i live in the city because it is more convinient to look for a jobs, and in city has better education, healthcare system and facilities with higher life quality However, when i am older i want to come back to my countryside because it is very peaceful with fresh environment. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-69.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: City vs Countryside</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is best about city life?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is best about city life?
-> It is more convinient. I can look for jobs easily, i have better education, healthcare systems and facility. The transport is developing so i can move quicklier. Overall, It has higher life quality (living standard). 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-69.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: City vs Countryside</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is best about country life?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is best about countryside life?
It has better lifestyle because in countryside people often have slower lifestyle, they usually do excercise in the morning, seldom eat fastfood. It also has fresh environment with many trees, river, lake. It is peaceful and beautiful. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-70.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Modern Architecture</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you like glass buildings?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you like glass buildings ?.
I really like glass buildings. because they look modern and elegant. when i enter the buildings i feel professional. 

</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-70.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Modern Architecture</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is old building better?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is old building better ? Modern Architecture.
I think old building is better because it is historic and unique. They are often large with a gadern and a lake outside when i am older i want to leave there. It reminds me of old childhood memories.    
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-70.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Modern Architecture</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What makes a building beautiful?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-71.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Holidays</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What is your favorite holiday?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What is your favorite holiday?
I think it is Tet Holiday. because it is one of the most famous traditional holiday in my country and i currently leave far from my house so i want to have longer holiday to come back to hometown and spend time with family. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-71.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Holidays</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How do you celebrate it?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How do you celebrate it ? Holidays
-> I usually come back to my hometown and prepare it with my parents like On the morning, i buy some flowers to decorate my house, make hand-made foods. I also visit my neighbour and relatives and wish for lucks.   
At night, we gather together arround the fire to have small talks with each other
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-71.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Holidays</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is holiday time for family?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is holiday time for family ?.
Yes, absolutely. During the years, family members live in different countries so we seldom have a chance to meet each other. Tet holiday is the only opportunity to gather and come back home.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-72.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Public Libraries</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Are they still useful?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Are they still useful ? Public Libraries
-> Not entirely, people used to go to library to look for books. 
But now, in modern world, we can find any books on the Internet. It is very convinient. there are many options to choose. I can read anywhere anytime on my phone for free without carrying heavy books.
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-72.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Public Libraries</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">What can we find there besides books?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> What can we find there besides books ? Public Libraries
Beside books, we can find newpapers, magazines, ... Some libraries are equiped with computers. 
</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-72.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
