                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Public Libraries</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Should they be free?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Should they be free? Public Libraries.
Yes, of course because more people can access to libraries and it's books. This will helps students who are in poor conditions and do not have money to buy books. It will promote education among the students. 

