                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Energy Saving</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">How can we save energy?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How can we save energy?
